<h2 class="bold font-l">Queen Elsa of Arendelle</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Elsa was born with ice magic. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnIcePerson" class='trope-example-link'>An Ice Person</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="roao78" data-video-descrip="The opening song &amp;quot;Frozen Heart&amp;quot; vaguely foreshadows the entire plot of the movie, from Elsa being born of ice powers, the endless winter, and Anna getting a frozen heart." data-video-title="Frozen Heart" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/roao78_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/roao78.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/Foreshadowing" data-video-tropename="Foreshadowing" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/Frozen2013" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/roao78.jpg">
